2. Clarinet: The Core Tool for Local Development

Clarinet is the standard toolkit for writing, testing, and deploying Clarity smart contracts.

What you can do:

Spin up a local Stacks devnet instantly

Write unit tests in JavaScript or Rust

Simulate block production

Deploy contract packages

Generate automated coverage reports

Clarinet is the equivalent of “Hardhat for Stacks,” but with tighter integration to the blockchain model.
